name: Master Data Statistics
query:
SELECT SUBSTRING(table_name, 4) as DocType, d.module as 'Module', table_rows as `Number of Rows`
    FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.TABLES t
    LEFT OUTER JOIN `tabDocType` d ON d.name = SUBSTRING(t.table_name, 4)
    WHERE table_rows > 0
      AND SUBSTRING(table_name, 4) IN (SELECT name FROM tabDocType WHERE is_submittable != 1 and istable = 0)
    ORDER BY table_rows DESC
